  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    PM returns to Salisbury on anniversary of Novichok poisoning
  </h1>
</div>

  </div>
  
  <div class="column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph ">
    Prime Minister Theresa May visited Salisbury exactly a year after a chemical weapon was used on the streets of the city.
  </p>

  </div>
</div>

<div class="grid-row">
  <div class="metadata-logo-wrapper">
    <div class="column-two-thirds metadata-column">
